Using bluetooth module HC-05 and mobile app called 'Arduino bluetooth control' for controlling lights, fans and any electric divices with voice commands from phone.

Arduino can only provide 5V output voltage so you need to use 5V relay switch to play with AC current devides!

(Link for app: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.broxcode.arduinobluetoothfree)
